rows.label: qst640409_msg0001
rows.name:
Wowee... Now this is what I expect
when it comes to hot springs!

rows.label: qst640409_msg0002
rows.name:
We are not appeased... This place is
not maintained at all! Where is the
landscaping? The facilities? The staff?

rows.label: qst640409_msg0003
rows.name:
What point is there to winning a
lifetime of free entry when it's
free to enter to begin with?!

rows.label: qst640409_msg0004
rows.name:
There, there, Rinne. Lighten up!
We've walked all this way, might
as well try to enjoy ourselves.

rows.label: qst640409_msg0006
rows.name:
A banquet with our beautiful
friends in the hot spring!
This day may yet be salvaged!

rows.label: qst640409_msg0101
rows.name:
Meleph-sama, I've heard of this
place. The water here will do
wonders for your skin, believe me.

rows.label: qst640409_msg0102
rows.name:
Is that so? I'm looking forward to it...
To think, all this time in Superbia and
we've never once visited here.

rows.label: qst640409_msg0103
rows.name:
Okay Seori, if you see
any Peeping Toms, you've
gotta end them quickly.

rows.label: qst640409_msg0104
rows.name:
They'll be dead before
they can blink...

rows.label: qst640409_msg0105
rows.name:
It's all right, Kaku-tan and
Suke-tan are happy to keep
watch! Aren't you, guys?

rows.label: qst640409_msg0106
rows.name:
I don't think I've ever had a
banquet in a hot spring before,
but I bet it'll be awesome fun!

rows.label: qst640409_msg0107
rows.name:
I know, right? I'm
already feeling happy!

rows.label: qst640409_msg0108
rows.name:
[ML:Feeling kind=Anger ]These filthy beasts are in
the way of our admiring our
beloved companions!!!

rows.label: qst640409_msg0109
rows.name: [ML:Feeling kind=Anger ]We will not stand for thiiiiiis!!!
